⍝ MatrixDivide.tc
⍝ ═══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A B simple numeric rank≤2; B full column rank
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (1↓⍴B),1↓⍴A
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 2) (,0 0 1 0 0)
      B ← 0.1×⎕RVAL 2 (3 3) (,0 0 1 0 0)    ⍝ float for stability
      B ← B+(3 3⍴3 0 0 0 3 0 0 0 3)         ⍝ ensure dominant diagonal
      Z ← A⌹B
      (⍴Z) ≡ (1↓⍴B),1↓⍴A
1
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ,1⌈¯2+(⍴⍴A)+⍴⍴B
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,1⌈¯2+(⍴⍴A)+⍴⍴B
1
